時候都唔小心吸咗入鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實陣味都幾難聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32207d38cff10216cb50dd88018a74dc9f240c74","tid":20784,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:39:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買完先發現好難飲咁點算</blockquote><br />\n我經驗，逢親買左啲味道難飲既粉，用維他奶shake都會變好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用豆奶溝whey會破壞蛋白質, 飲左變無飲 , 用鮮奶開啦"},{"pid":"83d651d3400e6f73dfb6569af4f9a332716eb8b8","tid":20784,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:41:18.000Z","msg":"其實小肥就減肥先啦 , 洗鬼咁快飲粉咩"},{"pid":"b1a57550feea83f25cf65b3989d1c50949bc6334","tid":20784,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日攝取自己體重1.5-2倍份量嘅蛋白質，睇下你嗰日飲食差幾多再補翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實條數只係生產商吹嘅上限 , 目的想你飲快啲 , 其實1kg對1g已經夠, 另外就咁用重量直接計係錯的, 計埋脂肪重量去計飲用量覺唔覺有啲唔合理 ?<br />\n<br />\n計飲用量起碼都要知自己個體脂先啦"},{"pid":"2322913480a92fa1dced9a5029ff0201a71f024e","tid":20784,"uid":40950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b2161ddb2d4b4d2e1269de84b3226c309dfe2f4c","tid":20784,"uid":51594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每日攝取自己體重1.5-2倍份量嘅蛋白質，睇下你嗰日飲食差幾多再補翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實條數只係生產商吹嘅上限 , 目的想你飲快啲 , 其實1kg對1g已經夠, 另外就咁用重量直接計係錯的, 計埋脂肪重量去計飲用量覺唔覺有啲唔合理 ?<br />\n<br />\n計飲用量起碼都要知自己個體脂先啦</blockquote><br />\n巴打你講得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頭先查咗查都發覺計埋體脂準啲<br />\n我之前睇Ptt個健身版都見到有鄉民嘅心得，都有參考價值<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1315710748480741&amp;id=1131